column1: I hope the President & First Lady have a swift & complete recovery.   It’s a reminder to everyone to wear a mask wash your hands social distance & take COVID-19 seriously.

Proud to announce this #COVID19 funding for local tech company @Luminostics.  It is hoped that this project can help keep our healthcare workers safe provide relief for cash-strapped local governments & provide convenience & assurance for families. https://t.co/ud3mXGeNGB

With his latest Exec Order limiting immigration to the U.S. the President is once again abusing the law in an attempt to distract the American public from his abject failure to combat COVID-19.  Reminder to the Trump Admin: Congress writes the laws  https://t.co/U53QB4OkbV
Do you have specific questions about the #HeroesAct?  The latest #COVID19 update on my website includes topic-by-topic resources on the House-passed bill.  https://t.co/9kICxt2M1O

California is providing disaster relief for undocumented immigrants impacted by the #COVID19 pandemic.  If you live in Santa Clara County you may be eligible.   Here are details from @CatholicCharSCC ⤵️ https://t.co/VpRtITNd5f

WATCH LIVE NOW  We're holding a @HouseJudiciary virtual roundtable on the Trump Admin's mishandling of the immigration detention system in the face of the deadly #COVID19 pandemic.  Sadly @ICEgov's actions have endangered lives in the U.S. & abroad.  https://t.co/R2pSi5tLqY

TOMORROW 12:30pmET/9:30amPT  @HouseJudiciary virtual roundtable on @ICEgov's #COVID19 response & conditions in detention facilities  ➡️https://t.co/C0S1KS9Zrt⬅️  @RepJerryNadler @RepJayapal @RepLouCorrea @RepSylviaGarcia @RepJoeNeguse @RepDMP @RepEscobar @JacksonLeeTX18 @RepMGS

.@HealthySCC has created multilingual videos about #COVID19.  Take a look at the playlist page to find the language series that you prefer: https://t.co/j98UPIYtbL

🗣️ Our state wants your input 🗣️   @CAgovernor @GavinNewsom is asking Californians to help by providing comments on the roadmap for community resiliency. This will inform how modifications are made to the #COVID19 Stay-at-Home order ⤵️  https://t.co/4gqUCnYu8K

ICYMI - Latest Santa Clara County #COVID19 fed relief:  🏫 $44.5M+ for @SJSU @DeAnza_College @OfficialEVC @GavilanCollege @SJCityCollege  ✈️ $65.6M+ for @FlySJC  Glad our local families workers students & businesses are starting to get this $$ to help meet community needs.
NEIGHBORS: You can now dial 2-1-1 for #COVID19 answers all day every day. https://t.co/SESf1LXRqi

💻NEW PAGE FOR STUDENTS & TEACHERS💻  There are tons of *free* digital resources for kids & parents who are sheltering in place & #COVID19 emergency education-related info available for families.  I've put nat'l & local resources in one place here⤵️ https://t.co/9FINcApZfc https://t.co/q7i2tI2NQ1

This is good news. Thank you Santa Clara County!   Let's be cautiously optimistic & keep these positive trends going. How? By continuing to follow the #COVID19 #ShelterInPlace orders & the advice of medical professionals.  #ApartTogetherSCC https://t.co/HTIZvwlk1e
